<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>
        <%= certificationName %> Certification
    </title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            background-color: #f4f7f6;
            color: #333;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 20px;
            text-align: center;
        }

        .container {
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: auto;
            background-color: #fff;
            padding: 40px;
            border-radius: 10px;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 8px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
        }

        h1 {
            color: #1a4d85;
        }

        form {
            margin-top: 30px;
        }

        input[type="text"] {
            width: 80%;
            padding: 12px;
            margin-top: 10px;
            border: 1px solid #ccc;
            border-radius: 5px;
        }

        button {
            background-color: #28a745;
            color: white;
            padding: 14px 20px;
            margin-top: 20px;
            border: none;
            border-radius: 5px;
            cursor: pointer;
            font-size: 16px;
        }

        button:hover {
            background-color: #218838;
        }

        .instructions {
            text-align: left;
            margin-top: 20px;
        }

        ul {
            list-style-type: disc;
            padding-left: 20px;
        }
    </style>
</head>

<body>
    <div class="container">
        <h1>
            <%= certificationName %> Certification
        </h1>
        <p>To begin, please enter your name. Your name will appear on the certificate if you pass.</p>
        <form action="/start-quiz" method="post">
            <input type="hidden" name="certificationName" value="<%= certificationName %>">
            <input type="text" name="userName" placeholder="Enter your full name" required>
            <div class="instructions">
                <h3>Instructions:</h3>
                <ul>
                    <li>The quiz consists of 10 questions.</li>
                    <li>You must answer at least 6 questions correctly to pass.</li>
                    <li>The questions include theory, code dry-runs, and multiple-choice.</li>
                    <li>You will be given one question at a time.</li>
                </ul>
            </div>
            <button type="submit">Start Quiz</button>
            <button><a style="text-decoration: none; color: #f4f7f6;" href="/CodeRido/certificate">Quit</a></button>
            
        </form>
    </div>
</body>

</html>